### Testar API PulseTap Backend
### Execute estes comandos no VS Code com extensão REST Client ou use curl

### 1. Testar se API está funcionando
GET http://localhost:8080/api/auth/test

### 2. Registrar novo usuário
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "teste@exemplo.com",
  "firstName": "João",
  "lastName": "Silva",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 3. Fazer login com usuário de teste
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@pulsetap.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 4. Fazer login com outro usuário de teste
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@pulsetap.com",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 5. Verificar se email existe
GET http://localhost:8080/api/auth/check-email/admin@pulsetap.com

### 6. Listar todos os usuários
GET http://localhost:8080/api/auth/users

### 7. Obter perfil do usuário (substitua TOKEN pelo token retornado no login)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/user/profile
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_AQUI

### 8. Verificar token
GET http://localhost:8080/api/user/verify-token
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_AQUI

### 9. Atualizar perfil (substitua TOKEN pelo token retornado no login)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/user/profile
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_AQUI
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Nome Atualizado",
  "lastName": "Sobrenome Atualizado"
}

### Exemplo de teste com curl (copie e cole no terminal):

### Testar API
curl -X GET http://localhost:8080/api/auth/test

### Registrar usuário
curl -X POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "email": "novo@usuario.com",
    "firstName": "Novo",
    "lastName": "Usuário",
    "password": "123456"
  }'

### Fazer login
curl -X POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "email": "admin@pulsetap.com",
    "password": "123456"
  }'

### Obter perfil (substitua TOKEN pelo token retornado)
curl -X GET http://localhost:8080/api/user/profile \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer TOKEN_AQUI"
